- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the implementation of optimization algorithms, which are a type of algorithm commonly studied in this sub-category.

- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper discusses the design decisions made in building the library, which is relevant to software engineering.
